SD.1 StructureDefinition-q

source file: source/pages/_includes/q-intro.md

The Argonaut Q pofile sets the minimum expectations for the Q resource to record, search and fetch Q for simple assessments, surveys, etc as defined in this implementation guide

Scope and Usage

The Argonaut Questionnaire resource supports:

  • Instructions for Subjects (“form filler outers”)
  • Instructions for the Providers (e., Scoring instructions)
  • Text based questions
    • Including standardized concepts like LOINC
  • Answers
    • T/F, multiple choice (Including standardized concepts like LOINC)
    • hort answer, narrative, etc
  • Provisions for scoring of answers
    • Textual based description how to calculate the total scores
    • Associated scores for each question-answer/answer choice
  • Other Details like whether required or not, Provider instructions hidden or not, etc.`

Mandatory Data Elements and Terminology

The following data-elements are mandatory (i.e data MUST be present). blah blah blah

 {
   "resourceType" : "Questionnaire",
    "id" : "<id>", // Logical id of this artifact
    "meta" : {Meta}, // Metadata about the resource
    "implicitRules" : "<uri>", // A set of rules under which this content was created
    "language" : "<code>", // Language of the resource content
    "text" : {Narrative}, // Text summary of the resource, for human interpretation
    "contained" : [{Resource}], // Contained, inline Resources
    "extension": [
    ],
    "url" : "<uri>", // Logical URI to reference this questionnaire (globally unique)
    "identifier" : [{Identifier}], // Additional identifier for the questionnaire
    "version" : "<string>", // Business version of the questionnaire
    "name" : "<string>", // Name for this questionnaire (computer friendly)
    "title" : "<string>", // Name for this questionnaire (human friendly)
    "status" : "<code>", // R! draft | active | retired | unknown
    "experimental" : <boolean>, // For testing purposes, not real usage
    "date" : "<dateTime>", // Date this was last changed
    "publisher" : "<string>", // Name of the publisher (organization or individual)
    "description" : "<markdown>", // Natural language description of the questionnaire
    "purpose" : "<markdown>", // Why this questionnaire is defined
    "approvalDate" : "<date>", // When the questionnaire was approved by publisher
    "lastReviewDate" : "<date>", // When the questionnaire was last reviewed
    "effectivePeriod" : {Period}, // When the questionnaire is expected to be used
    "useContext" : [{UsageContext}], // Context the content is intended to support
    "jurisdiction" : [{CodeableConcept}], // Intended jurisdiction for questionnaire (if applicable)
    "contact" : [{ContactDetail}], // Contact details for the publisher
    "copyright" : "<markdown>", // Use and/or publishing restrictions
    "code" : [{Coding}], // Concept that represents the overall questionnaire
    "subjectType" : ["<code>"], // Resource that can be subject of QuestionnaireResponse
    "item" : [{ // C? Questions and sections within the Questionnaire
      "extension": [
      ],
      "linkId" : "<string>", // R! Unique id for item in questionnaire
      "definition" : "<uri>", // ElementDefinition - details for the item
      "code" : [{Coding}], // Corresponding concept for this item in a terminology
      "prefix" : "<string>", // E.g. "1(a)", "2.5.3"
      "text" : "<string>", // Primary text for the item
      "type" : "<code>", // R! group | display | boolean | decimal | integer | date | dateTime +
      "enableWhen" : [{ // C? Only allow data when
        "extension": [
        ],
        "question" : "<string>", // R! Question that determines whether item is enabled
        "hasAnswer" : <boolean>, // Enable when answered or not
// value[x]: Value question must have. One of these 12:
        "answerBoolean" : <boolean>, // Value question must have
        "answerDecimal" : <decimal> // Value question must have
        "answerInteger" : <integer>, // Value question must have
        "answerDate" : "<date>", // Value question must have
        "answerDateTime" : "<dateTime>", // Value question must have
        "answerTime" : "<time>", // Value question must have
        "answerString" : "<string>", // Value question must have
        "answerUri" : "<uri>", // Value question must have
        "answerAttachment" : {Attachment}, // Value question must have
        "answerCoding" : {Coding}, // Value question must have
        "answerQuantity" : {Quantity}, // Value question must have
        "answerReference" : {Reference(Resource)}, // Value question must have
      }],
      "required" : <boolean>, // Whether the item must be included in data results
      "repeats" : <boolean>, // Whether the item may repeat
      "readOnly" : <boolean>, // Don't allow human editing
      "maxLength" : <integer>, // No more than this many characters
      "options" : {Reference(ValueSet)}, // Valueset containing permitted answers
      "option" : [{ // C? Permitted answer
        "extension": [
        ],
// value[x]: Answer value. One of these 5:
        "valueInteger" : <integer>, // R! Answer value
        "valueDate" : "<date>" // R! Answer value
        "valueTime" : "<time>", // R! Answer value
        "valueString" : "<string>", // R! Answer value
        "valueCoding" : {Coding}, // R! Answer value
      }],
// value[x]: Default value when item is first rendered. One of these 12:
      "initialBoolean" : <boolean>, // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialDecimal" : <decimal>, // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialInteger" : <integer> // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialDate" : "<date>", // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialDateTime" : "<dateTime>", // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialTime" : "<time>", // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialString" : "<string>", // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialUri" : "<uri>", // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialAttachment" : {Attachment}, // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialCoding" : {Coding}, // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialQuantity" : {Quantity}, // Default value when item is first rendered
      "initialReference" : {Reference(Resource)}, // Default value when item is first rendered
// value[x]: Nested questionnaire items. One of these 0:
    }],
  }
